---
title: Cherry-Glazed Steak & Spiced Roast Veggies with Tomato Salad
description: Round out the day with this spectacular steak, drizzled with a sticky-sweet cherry glaze. And for the real 'cherry' on top, we’ve added mildly-spiced roast veggies and a refreshing garden salad for crispiness and depth of flavour to boot!
